<p>To assist developers that manage the codebase for RocketSpace, a component guide was also created containing sample code for quick copy and pasting abilities. To keep components to their most basic form, minimal styling was given allowing for further customizing based on unique contexts. This is based on the principle of "<a href="http://v3.danielmall.com/articles/content-display-patterns">Content vs. Display Patterns</a>" written by Dan Mall.</p>
