<h3>The Final product</h3>
<p>After mutliple feedback sessions it was decided the logo was lacking an element. An element that could be used in social media situations such as an avatar since using text alone would not be legible in those types of situations. To remain true to the ideals of simplistic, a typographic element was used to create an abstract shape.</p>
